title: America's Thrift Store hit by cyber attack, Birmingham-based company says credit card data exposed
text:
Published By: Al.com: Mobile - Today 
Cyber hackers used malware to obtain person information on shoppers at America's Thrift Store, the Birmingham-based company has announced....
